    • ViewHolder

      public ViewHolder(android.view.View itemView, RvInterface rvInterface)
      Constructs a ViewHolder for items in a RecyclerView with associated views and a RecyclerView interface for item click events.
      参数:
      itemView - The root view representing an item in the RecyclerView.
      rvInterface - The RecyclerView interface for handling item click events.
